            "pub_date": "2025-06-05 23:30:07",
            "source": "cnyes",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "id": 6009163,
            "title": "美股三大股指由跌轉漲，納指現漲0.33%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>BlockBeats 消息，6 月 5 日，根據行情數據，美股三大股指由跌轉漲，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道指</a>收復跌幅、<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">標普 500 指數</a>現漲 0.12%、納指現漲 0.33%。 </p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://m.theblockbeats.info/tw/flash/297059\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color:#A9A9A9\">原文連結</a></p></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6009163",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-05 23:30:07",
            "source": "cnyes",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
