        {
            "id": 6009140,
            "title": "90分鐘熱線！川普曝：習近平邀請我訪中 雙邊貿易協議再加溫",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國總統川普周四 (5 日) 在社群平台 Truth Social 發文表示，他已與中國國家主席習近平進行了一通約 90 分鐘的電話會談，雙方討論了最近達成的貿易協議細節，並同意盡快安排新一輪會談，地點尚待決定。川普形容，這次對話「結果對兩國都非常正面」，同時也解決了稀土產品的複雜性問題。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009140%2Fl%2F7310acf92bb504e2c32081f374adc49d.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">川普與習近平通話約一個半小時 聚焦貿易協議細節(圖：REUTERS/TPG)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普指出，美方將派出財政部長貝森特 (Scott Bessent)、商務部長盧特尼克(Howard Lutnick) 及美國貿易代表葛里爾 (Jamieson Greer) 參加新一輪會談。他強調，這次通話「幾乎完全聚焦在貿易問題」，並未涉及俄羅斯、烏克蘭或伊朗事務。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>稍早，中國外交部及中國駐美大使館證實，這通電話是由川普主動提出的。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>此外，川普透露，習近平在通話中親切邀請他和第一夫人訪問中國，他也予以積極回應，強調雙方作為「兩個偉大國家的總統」對此行都非常期待。川普最後表示，相關會議的時間與地點將在稍後向媒體公布，並感謝外界的關注。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img alt=\"圖：川普Truth Social\" data-height=\"581\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.0516351118760758\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6009140/m/6fbfb8c7322741e044f04458b623d142.jpg\" data-width=\"611\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6009140/l/6fbfb8c7322741e044f04458b623d142.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption>圖：川普 Truth Social</figcaption>\n</figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>持續更新....</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
